CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C2, reads: "Happy - Enjoying a joke are award winners (left to right): Miss Martha Tyson, Businesswoman; Mrs. Eunice Cook, Humanities; Councilman James A. Jordon, and Mrs. Mary Jane Page, Sororities."
TitMainTitle: Martha Tyson, Eunice Cook, James A. Jordon, and Mary Jane Page, gathered in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall for Pittsburgh Courier newspaper's Appreciation Day rally
